    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create visual effects in this particle-based editor! Import the effects into your favorite game engine and fill your game world with colorful animations using the <strong>runtime plugins</strong> or by rendering them to <strong>sprite sheets</strong>, <strong>image sequences</strong> and <strong>videos</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734820/extras/b1ac289f7c2adc8f4a5f70a1e8201d8d.webp?t=1767347154\" width=200 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design 2D and 3D visual effects in a matter of minutes using Pixelpart's intuitive particle-based workflow. Pixelpart offers a variety of features to bring your effects to life like force fields, colliders, keyframe animations, motion paths and custom materials.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734820/extras/78d045658094b0f836a7f500131382a6.webp?t=1767347154\" width=200 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using Pixelpart's game engine plugins, directly import effects into the engine and control them via scripts. You can download plugins for these game engines on the Pixelpart website: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unity Engine (Unity 2021.3+)</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Godot (Godot 4.3+)</strong> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734820/extras/8199a149f353ddfe29fa34a63e10abca.webp?t=1767347154\" width=200 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can export your effects to various formats: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sprite sheets</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Image sequences and GIFs</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Videos</strong> </p></li></ul>",
